Educational book Chandler and Grants Glaucoma, Fifth Edition handed out at Vision Source at Maximize Your OCT Potential 2.0 Advanced Imaging on April 29 2015

Physicians are provided modest meals during the course of doing business with Carl Zeiss Meditec Inc. The physician could be attending or presenting at an educational presentation, a product training session or being invited for a meal to provide feedback on our products. The total cost of meals are averaged across attendees. This meal took place at Vision Source Zeiss Symposium Maximize Your OCT Potential 2.0 Advanced Imaging on April 29 2015
